  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dba \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Pohottuva's official support to Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The General Secretary of Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna, Member of Parliament Mr. Aegina Sagara Kariyawasam says in a statement that Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna will support Acting President Ranil Wickramasinghe during the election of the President to be held on the 20th in Parliament.",
        "Mr. Kariyawasam has further said that with the decision that a member of Parliament of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna will run for the presidency, Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe has decided to support Mr. Wickramasinghe as he thinks that Mr. Wickramasinghe is the most suitable person for the presidency at this time. The announcement is given below."
      ],
